            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div class=\"akcelo-wrapper akcelo-video media--169\" style=\"width:100%\"><div class=\"border:solid 1px #C0C0C0\" id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\" video-id=\"k5jZONi8Bm1QssEd2cQ\"><div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta content=\"Accel Sees Room for AI Market to Grow\" itemprop=\"name\"/><meta content=\"Accel Partner Philippe Botteri discusses the venture firm's latest report on the global AI market and why AI spending and startup valuations will go even higher. He joins Caroline Hyde on &quot;Bloomberg Tech.&quot;\n\" itemprop=\"description\"/><meta content=\"2025-11-13T22:42:43+01:00\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/><meta content=\"/images/mtnewswires/A3505366.png\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/><meta content=\"https://geo.dailymotion.com/player/x80uo.html?video=k5jZONi8Bm1QssEd2cQ\" itemprop=\"embedUrl\"/></div></div></div>\n               Accel Partner Philippe Botteri discusses the venture firm's latest report on the global AI market and why AI spending and startup valuations will go even higher. He joins Caroline Hyde on \"Bloomberg Tech.\"<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51673166');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
